- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper uses supervised and unsupervised learning techniques. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with developing technology for languages where no transcribed data is available. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing speech signals.
